Example(Bypass SQL Injection Protection):

PHPNuke + NukeSentinel
http://localhost/php-nuke/?%2f**%2fUNION%2f**%2fSELECT ... etc

Nuke-Evolution + NukeSentinel
http://localhost/nuke-evolution/?%2f**%2fUNION%2f**%2fSELECT .. etc



